member.name: WS_ANY_ATTRIBUTES
member.summary: This type is used to store a set of attributes that have not been directly mapped to field of a structure.

member.name: WS_ANY_ATTRIBUTES.attributes
member.summary: An array of attributes. This field may be NULL if attributeCount is zero.

member.name: WS_ANY_ATTRIBUTES.attributeCount
member.summary: The number of attributes in the array.
